HEADWORD: honky
<hw>honky</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A white (caucasian)
person; -- a term used by some African-Americans, intended to be
disparaging and often taken as offensive.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>honkie</asp> and <asp>honkey</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> whitey.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

